{"id": 232025800, "title": "Expert Speaks On Data Driven Solutions To Aid Business Sustainability", "text": "Clement Odooh, a seasoned Data Engineer, Business Intelligence specialist, and Data Visualization expert, has emphasized the importance of data-driven decision support systems in empowering businesses to make informed choices and gain actionable insights. Disclosing in a media statement,he said with over seven years of industry experience in the IT data industry, he has developed a passion for crafting solutions that unlock the true potential of an organization\u2019s data, driving efficiency, optimizing processes, and ultimately propelling them towards success. He noted further that his expertise has enabled businesses to harness the power of their information, providing enhanced decision-making through data visualization, improved operational efficiency with data analytics, and actionable insights for strategic planning. He said: \u201cTo stay ahead in the rapidly evolving data field, one must engage in continuous learning, hands-on exploration, client feedback loops, and industry engagement. I believe that the industry can thrive by bridging the data divide, prioritizing ethical considerations, focusing on explainable AI, embracing collaboration, and nurturing diverse talent.\u201d He stated. Odooh opined that government can play a vital role in promoting the industry by investing in data infrastructure, supporting research and development, promoting data literacy, establishing clear data governance frameworks, and facilitating public-private partnerships. He added that his commitment to empowering businesses through data-driven solutions makes him a valuable asset in the industry.", "summary": "<div style=\"margin-bottom:20px;\"><img width=\"222\" height=\"333\" src=\"https://independent.ng/wp-content/uploads/IMG-20240609-WA0001-1.jpg\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\"